{"image_id": "PKI_2013_page_82", "image_size": [1238, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "NOTES TO CONSOLIDATED FINANCIAL STATEMENTS — (Continued)", "bbox": [274.3, 140.2, 963.6, 161.0]}, {"text": "Acquisition in fiscal year 2012", "bbox": [164.6, 190.2, 426.7, 211.0]}, {"text": "Acquisition of Haoyuan Biotech Co., Ltd. In November 2012, the Company acquired all outstanding stock of", "bbox": [185.5, 227.7, 1094.2, 248.8]}, {"text": "Shanghai Haoyuan Biotech Co., Ltd. (“Haoyuan”). Haoyuan is a provider of nucleic acid-based blood screening", "bbox": [143.8, 252.9, 1094.0, 273.8]}, {"text": "solutions for the blood banking and clinical diagnostics markets. The Company expects this acquisition to extend", "bbox": [143.8, 277.9, 1094.1, 298.8]}, {"text": "the Company’s capabilities into nucleic acid blood screening, as well as deepen its position in the growing", "bbox": [143.8, 302.9, 1094.2, 323.8]}, {"text": "molecular clinical diagnostics market in China. The Company paid the shareholders of Haoyuan $38.0 million in", "bbox": [143.8, 328.0, 1094.2, 348.8]}, {"text": "cash for the stock of Haoyuan. The Company recorded a receivable of $2.7 million from the shareholders of", "bbox": [143.8, 353.0, 1094.2, 373.8]}, {"text": "Haoyuan as a reduction of purchase price for the settlement of certain contingencies. This receivable was", "bbox": [143.8, 378.0, 1094.2, 398.8]}, {"text": "collected in fiscal year 2013. As of the closing date, the Company potentially had to pay the shareholders", "bbox": [143.8, 403.0, 1094.0, 423.8]}, {"text": "additional contingent consideration of up to $30.0 million, which at closing had an estimated fair value of $1.9", "bbox": [143.8, 428.0, 1094.2, 448.8]}, {"text": "million. The excess of the purchase price over the fair value of the acquired net assets represents cost and", "bbox": [143.8, 453.0, 1094.2, 473.8]}, {"text": "revenue synergies specific to the Company, as well as non-capitalizable intangible assets, such as the employee", "bbox": [143.8, 478.0, 1094.1, 498.8]}, {"text": "workforce acquired, and has been allocated to goodwill, none of which is tax deductible. The Company reported", "bbox": [143.8, 503.0, 1094.0, 523.8]}, {"text": "the operations for this acquisition within the results of the Company’s Human Health segment from the", "bbox": [143.8, 528.0, 1094.1, 548.9]}, {"text": "acquisition date.", "bbox": [143.8, 553.0, 280.7, 573.9]}, {"text": "The total purchase price has been allocated to the estimated fair values of assets acquired and liabilities", "bbox": [185.5, 603.0, 1093.8, 623.9]}, {"text": "assumed as follows:", "bbox": [143.8, 628.0, 311.9, 648.9]}, {"text": "Haoyuan", "bbox": [968.5, 672.7, 1033.4, 689.4]}, {"text": "(In thousands)", "bbox": [949.3, 697.7, 1052.6, 714.4]}, {"text": "Fair value of business combination:", "bbox": [185.5, 719.7, 483.4, 740.6]}, {"text": "Cash payments . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [227.2, 744.7, 918.1, 765.6]}, {"text": "$38,000", "bbox": [967.1, 744.7, 1034.8, 765.6]}, {"text": "Contingent consideration . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [227.2, 769.8, 918.1, 790.6]}, {"text": "1,900", "bbox": [987.9, 769.8, 1034.8, 790.6]}, {"text": "Working capital and other adjustments . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [227.2, 794.8, 918.1, 815.6]}, {"text": "(2,729)", "bbox": [980.9, 794.8, 1041.7, 815.6]}, {"text": "Less: cash acquired . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [227.2, 819.8, 918.1, 840.6]}, {"text": "(175)", "bbox": [996.5, 819.8, 1041.7, 840.6]}, {"text": "Total . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [227.2, 853.1, 918.1, 874.0]}, {"text": "$36,996", "bbox": [967.1, 853.1, 1034.8, 87